    "title": "AI Dungeon Generator",
    "desc": "I built an AI-driven dungeon generator inside <span class=\"syn-fn\">Unreal Engine</span> using <span class=\"syn-kw\">Deep Convolutional GANs</span> and <span class=\"syn-kw\">procedural algorithms</span>.",
    "about": "I built an AI-driven dungeon generation system that automatically creates coherent dungeon layouts inside Unreal Engine using deep learning and procedural algorithms.The core of the system was a DCGAN trained on dungeon layout data, augmented with 90°, 180°, and 270° rotations to improve generalisation. I also developed a series of corrective algorithms to clean and validate the generated layouts by enforcing room boundaries, placing doors between connected rooms, and using A* pathfinding to connect isolated regions into a single coherent dungeon.",
    "takeaways": "This project taught me how to bridge the gap between a trained ML model and a real game engine — something very few tutorials cover. The hardest part wasn't the model itself but making the output actually usable in a game context. I learned that post-processing and corrective systems are just as important as the model",
