    "desc": "My MSc dissertation — a novel NPC decision-making system combining <span class=\"syn-kw\">Utility AI</span> and <span class=\"syn-kw\">Deep Q-Learning</span> for <span class=\"syn-str\">smarter game behaviour</span>.",
